    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="hero-kicker">Kunstwandeling in Gits</p>

      <h1>
        <span>Kunst</span>
        <span>On(t)leed</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Een artistiek parcours waar bezoekers kunst, sfeer en ontmoeting samen
        kunnen beleven.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="home-section">
    <h2>Welkom</h2>
    <p>
      Welkom op de website van Kunst on(t)leed. Hier vind je binnenkort alle info
      over de kunstenaars, het parcours, de agenda en praktische afspraken.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="home-section">
    <h2>Ontdek het evenement</h2>
    <p>
      Kunst on(t)leed brengt kunst op een toegankelijke manier samen in een
      bijzonder parcours. Bezoekers kunnen verschillende kunstenaars ontdekken en
      onderweg genieten van de unieke sfeer van het evenement.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .poster-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 560px;
    padding: 3.6rem 0 2.2rem;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .texture {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 34% 18%, rgba(191, 160, 125, 0.18), transparent 18%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 36%, rgba(191, 160, 125, 0.12), transparent 26%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 58%, rgba(191, 160, 125, 0.1), transparent 18%);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .hero-art {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-art-desktop {
    opacity: 0.82;
  }

  .hero-art-mobile {
    display: none;
  }

  .hero-copy {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 620px;
    padding-top: 3.8rem;
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .poster-hero h1 {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.8rem, 7.2vw, 5.9rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    color: var(--title);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-top: 1.6rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .home-section {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .home-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
  }

  .home-section p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .poster-hero {
      min-height: 520px;
      padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 100%;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      max-width: 32rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .home-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .poster-hero {
      min-height: 26.9rem;
      padding: 1.05rem 0 0.15rem;
    }

    .hero-art-desktop {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero-art-mobile {
      display: block;
      opacity: 0.86;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 18rem;
      padding-top: 2.35rem;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 14.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.77rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .poster-hero h1 {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 13.9rem;
      font-size: clamp(3.05rem, 16vw, 4.2rem);
      line-height: 0.9;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 13.7rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.58;
    }

    .home-section {
      margin-top: 0.55rem;
    }

    .home-section h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .home-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .poster-hero {
      min-height: 25rem;
      padding: 0.95rem 0 0.025rem;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 17.2rem;
      padding-top: 2.15rem;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
      max-width: 13.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
    }

    .poster-hero h1 {
      max-width: 13.4rem;
      font-size: clamp(2.9rem, 15.4vw, 4rem);
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      max-width: 13.1rem;
      margin-top: 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
  }
</style>